import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='delay', kde=True, color='blue', bins=30)
    plt.axvline(data['delay'].median(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f"Median: {data['delay'].median():.2f}")
    plt.title("What is the distribution of delay time?", wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel("Delay Time")
    plt.ylabel("Frequency")
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    
    average_distance = data['distance'].mean()
    
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.barplot(x='origin', y='distance', data=data, ci=None)
    plt.axhline(y=average_distance, color='r', linestyle='--', label=f'Average Distance: {average_distance:.2f}')
    plt.title('What is the average distance traveled by flights?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Origin')
    plt.ylabel('Distance')
    plt.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data_grouped = data.groupby(['origin', 'destination']).size().reset_index(name='destination_count')
    data_pivot = data_grouped.pivot('origin', 'destination', 'destination_count')
    
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 8))
    heatmap = sns.heatmap(data_pivot, cmap='YlGnBu', annot=True, fmt='.0f', linewidths=.5)
    plt.title('Which origin and destination pairs are the most common?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Destination')
    plt.ylabel('Origin')
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    data['date'] = data['date'].dt.strftime('%Y-%m-%d')
    
    flight_frequency = data.groupby('date')['destination_count'].sum().reset_index()
    
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
    sns.lineplot(x='date', y='destination_count', data=flight_frequency)
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flight frequency by date?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Date')
    plt.ylabel('Flight Frequency')
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
